/td><td>0.02</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3448</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.68</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>3.03</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.77 / 1.64</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2012</th><th>2013</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>0.17</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-1.34</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.22</span></td><td>0.02</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.09</span></td><td>0.43</td><td>0.4</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">3.23</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">3.16</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.49</span></td><td>1.39</td><td>0.69</td><td>1.49</td><td>1.91</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">4.19</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>ryminusema252</code></td><td>展期收益EMA</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>inventory_21</code></td><td>库存(21日)</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 42 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 42 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>57</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3086</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>94.7%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>30.7</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p><strong>库存因子:</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">f_{inv,i,t} = -\\text{zscore}_{252}\\left(\\text{inventory\\_21}_{i,t}\\right)</div>\n<p>取反使低库存(相对历史)映射为正信号(做多)。</p>\n<p><strong>展期收益因子:</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">f_{carry,i,t} = \\text{ryminusema252}_{i,t}</div>\n<p>展期收益的252日EMA偏差,正值表示backwardation加深(近月强于远月)。</p>\n<p><strong>组合信号:</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{combo}_{i,t} = \\frac{1}{2}\\left[\\text{rank}_{cs}(f_{inv,i,t}) + \\text{rank}_{cs}(f_{carry,i,t})\\right]</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{rank}_{cs}</span> 为截面百分位排名 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\in [0,1]</span>,再线性映射到 <span class=\"math-tex\">[-1, +1]</span>。</p>\n<p><strong>仓位:</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{pos}_{i,t} = \\text{combo}_{i,t} \\times \\frac{\\sigma_{target}}{\\hat{\\sigma}_{i,t} \\times \\sqrt{252}} \\quad \\text{clip to } [-2, 2]</div>\n<p>每42个交易日再平衡,中间forward-fill。</p>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>诊断</th><th>行动</th><th>效果</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>基差方向错误(negated)导致basis因子负Sharpe; carry因子独大(1.13); combo负Sharpe</td><td>修正basis方向; 增加inventory z-score模式; 增加receipt/profit; 扩大参数网格</td><td>Best 1.13→1.46</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td>inv_zs252最佳(1.46)但与天风库存因子冗余(corr 0.80); combo4=1.20有潜力</td><td>聚焦combo优化: 6种组合方式(2/3/4/5/6因子), 多种权重, 更长hold(42-63)</td><td>Best 1.46→1.97</td></tr><tr><td>R3</td><td>combo2_ic_h42(inv+carry组合)=1.97; 冗余降至0.63; 所有gate通过; 3轮满足</td><td>完成</td><td>skip</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>关键转折</strong>: R2→R3的核心突破在于从单因子转向多因子组合。单独的inventory和carry因子都与因子库高度冗余(corr&gt;0.75),但将两者等权组合后,corr降至0.63且Sharpe从1.46提升至1.97。42日长hold也显著降低了换手率(0.42→0.19)。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全品种(56个活跃品种)</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 42日再平衡</li>\n<li><strong>数据依赖</strong>: <code>inventory_21</code>(70.9%非空率)和 <code>ryminusema252</code>(97.3%非空率)</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>: 与天风库存因子(20141201)相关性0.63,存在一定冗余; 2017和2023年Sharpe偏低(0.13/0.12)</li>\n<li><strong>信号稳定性</strong>: 半样本前半/后半均稳定; 76.8%品种时序IC为正</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>INV_ZSCORE_WINDOW</code></td><td><code>252</code></td><td>inventory_21 z-score lookback</td></tr><tr><td><code>HOLD_DAYS</code></td><td><code>42</code></td><td>rebalance hold period</td></tr><tr><td><code>VOL_TARGET</code></td><td><code>0.15</code></td><td>volatility target</td></tr><tr><td><code>MAX_LEVERAGE</code></td><td><code>2.0</code></td><td>max leverage</td></tr><tr><td><code>VOL_WINDOW</code></td><td><code>60</code></td><td>realized vol estimation window</td></tr><tr><td><code>MIN_PERIODS</code></td><td><code>20</code></td><td>min periods for vol estimation</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.24s</li>\n</ul>"}